dashboardItems.text:
*DEFINITIONS:*
Closing balance = Opening balance + Received - Distributed - Redistributed - Discarded -->Automatically  calculated indicator to count the remaining items at the end of the period
Stock on hand = physical stock count at the end of the period
Usable stock = Opening balance + received
Coverage time = Usable stock / Distributed + Discarded + Redistributed = nb. of months 

Stock discrepancy = Stock on hand - closing balance
     If discrepancy = 0 and 9 --> Stock on hand = closing balance (green cell) - acceptable discrepancy -
      If discrepancy < 0 --> closing balance > stock on hand (dark red cell)
      If discrepancy > 9 --> closing balance < stock on hand (light red cell)
